<!-- 
all pages listed by the menu should:
  - have defined unique page snippet: 
      - image with an url to an image representing this page
      - comment_link with an url to a place where one can comment
        you can also replace PAGE:_comment_link with something like
        {URL:{PAGE:aid}}#comments
        if you have installed comments from services like Disqus on a particular page.
  - be created with text editor like Ace, CKeditor or Markdown - they should not be created with block editor as we display full CONTENT of every page

you can remove { CONTENT: } flag to display only page description

the menu is limited to 10 last posts so you have to add pagination script
on the page displaying this menu with links to ?start=2 (posts 11-20) etc.
It should use {PAGE:subpages} flag to get number of all posts.
//-->
